{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 12''' is the 12th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events ==
== Births == * [[Shōan]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1301]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Morihiro Shinnō|ja|守邦親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 9th shōgun of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[1333]]). * [[Tenbun]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1534]] {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander (died [[1582]]). * [[Genroku]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1698]] {{ill|June 19|ja|6月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Aoki Kon'yō|ja|青木昆陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Rangaku scholar (died [[1769]]). * [[Tenmei]] 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1783]] {{ill|June 11|ja|6月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ryūtei Tanehiko|ja|柳亭種彦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a playwright (died [[1842]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1843]] {{ill|June 9|ja|6月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itō Yutaka|ja|伊東祐亨|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a naval officer (died [[1914]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1718]] {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tachibana Kitashi|ja|立花北枝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a haiku poet and one of the disciples of {{ill|Shōmon Jūtetsu|ja|正文宗十徹|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
