== Events ==
== Births == * [[:en:Shōan|Shōan]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1301|1301]] [[:en:June 19|June 19]]) – [[:en:Prince Morikuni|Morihiro Shinnō]], the 9th shōgun of the Kamakura shogunate (died [[:en:1333|1333]]). * [[:en:Tenbun|Tenbun]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1534|1534]] [[:en:June 23|June 23]]) – [[:en:Oda Nobunaga|Oda Nobunaga]], a military commander (died [[:en:1582|1582]]). * [[:en:Genroku|Genroku]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1698|1698]] [[:en:June 19|June 19]]) – [[:en:Aoki Konyō|Aoki Kon'yō]], a Rangaku scholar (died [[:en:1769|1769]]). * [[:en:Tenmei|Tenmei]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1783|1783]] [[:en:June 11|June 11]]) – {{ill|Ryūtei Tanehiko|ja|柳亭種彦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ryūtei Tanehiko|qq=}}, a playwright (died [[:en:1842|1842]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 14th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1843|1843]] [[:en:June 9|June 9]]) – [[:en:Itō Sukeyuki|Itō Yutaka]], a naval officer (died [[:en:1914|1914]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1718|1718]] [[:en:June 10|June 10]]) – {{ill|Tachibana Kitashi|ja|立花北枝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana Kitashi|qq=}}, a haiku poet and one of the disciples of {{ill|Shōmon Jūtetsu|ja|正文宗十徹|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōmon Jūtetsu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}.
